Template: whitelist-dnsmasq/whitelist-url
Type: string
Default: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LasEncinasIT/Whitelist-por-aula/main/Informatica%203.txt
Description: URL of the whitelist file:
 Enter the URL where the whitelist will be downloaded from.
 This URL should point to a plain text file with allowed domains.

Template: whitelist-dnsmasq/health-api-url
Type: string
Default:
Description: Health API URL (optional):
 Enter the URL of your health monitoring API, if you have one.
 Leave empty if you don't use centralized monitoring.

Template: whitelist-dnsmasq/health-api-secret
Type: password
Default:
Description: Health API secret (optional):
 Enter the shared secret for the health API.
 Leave empty if you don't use centralized monitoring.
